ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Oromocto Indian Reserve No. 26, New Brunswick
PrecisOrder setting apart 68.74 hectares (169.86 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Orocmocto First Nation as an addition to OROMOCTO INDIAN RESERVE No. 26, located in the County of Sunbury, approximately four kilometres from the Reserve, and borders the limits of the Town of Oromocto, in New Brunswick.
